snippet.title: Nubs' Adventure - Release Trailer iOS/Android
snippet.description:
App Store Link: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/nubs-adventure/id981935578
Google Play Link: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=nubs.adventure

Nubs' Adventure is platforming action and exploration combined with an intriguing story and a huge world to explore. All this on your iOS or Android device!
